    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Waves of Sound"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Nature, Innovation & Romantic Depth \r\n\r\nImmerse yourself in an unforgettable afternoon where stunning visuals, bold creativity, and timeless beauty collide.\r\n\r\nThe concert begins with Erica Procunier’s The Great Lakes Untamed - a breathtaking fusion of live orchestra and cinematic video, capturing the raw power and haunting majesty of North America’s inland seas. It’s a spellbinding journey through sound and image.\r\n\r\nFinally, settle into the lush emotional landscape of Brahms’ Symphony No. 3-a masterpiece of rich harmonies and introspective beauty that speaks straight to the soul.\r\n\r\nFrom wild waters to musical frontiers, this is a night of bold vision and deep feeling."
      }
    ],
